    "Finally, we emphasized that their participation was completely voluntary and that they could withdraw from the study at any point.",
    "Before we began the interviews, the participants had to sign a consent form outlining these terms to ensure their protection and the integrity of the study.",
    "In this section, we present the findings from our interviews.",
    "The analysis led to the creation of three themes, namely AI adoption (RQ1), environmental impact mitigation (RQ2), influence of regulations (RQ3).",
    "These themes were further organized into eight subthemes."
